value.name: LEGO Masters Korea
value.overview: Korean version of Lego Masters, it is the first new concept audition in Korea where Lego enthusiasts gather to have a brick assembly battle. There is a brain battle between geniuses who create a new world with small bricks. Korea's first special and amazing brick survival. Challenge the limits of Brick with outstanding technology and extraordinary ideas! Who will be the winner of the "Brick Master" trophy and prize money?
